# Custom policies for derived applications
# 
# This directory is for policies specific to your derived application.
# Files here should never exist in the base bioloop repository.
#
# To add a custom policy:
# 1. Create a new file (e.g., project.js)
# 2. Import core/builtin utilities as needed
# 3. Define and export a PolicyContainer
# 4. Register it in ../index.js POLICY_REGISTRY
#
# See ../custom/README.md for examples and guidelines
